data.description: This is a must-see! This home bas a great floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths. Great for a larger family or room for an office and guest room for a smaller family. There is a separate formal dining area and an open kitchen with new granite countertops overlooking the living room with a gas fireplace. New Luxury laminate flooring throughout the lower level, the exterior is newly painted and the interior is newly painted excluding bathrooms. Enjoy sitting and listening to a water feature in a fully landscaped backyard. Minutes from common area hiking trails and no rear neighbors.
